data.description:
Bright and Spacious 2 bedroom 2.5 bath townhome in sought after area of Smyrna! Close to so many amenities: Truist Park, shopping, highways, and restaurants.
This is an end unit with a fenced back yard. Living room with built ins surrounding the fireplace and a bay window.
Features off street parking for 2 vehicles.
To view register on the rently app.
 Tenant responsible for all utilities. 
Owner looking for 3x rent amount in applicant income. Looking for good rental history and good credit.
The Owner requires a 2-month Security deposit on all rentals or 
 we also offer a security Free option powered by Obligo for qualified applicants!
Please send income verification, 2 months of bank statements and driver's license to our email on our website after filling out an application.
All JNL Smart Realty residents are enrolled in the Resident Benefits Package (RBP) for $49.95/month.
which includes liability insurance, credit building to help boost the resident's credit score with timely rent payments, up to $1M Identity Theft Protection, HVAC air filter delivery (for applicable properties), move-in concierge service making utility connection and home service setup a breeze during your move-in, our best-in-class resident rewards program, on-demand pest control, and much more!
